text:
Everyone!
We're gonna give it our all!

Hmm... Doesn't that sound
a bit aggressive...?

Everyone!
Let's get even more hyped up!

(Huh...?
That voice... it's coming from the dressing room...)

Juri?
Were you calling for me-

Really?
I thought I heard your voice.

Oh... I was just doing vocal warm-ups
before the live performance...!!

Got to make sure my voice
is in good shape for singing, haha...!
